Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If a person catches a cold they will routinely go to the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:07.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but we would like to create an environment\Nin which more people will, similarly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,go to the psychiatrist's door without any sense of hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:14.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So when your mind gets weary,\Nplease, also do take a rest for the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino,\Nthank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:18.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Dr., there is something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:19.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that it's really worrying me, recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:22.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If so then I have some question too!\N{\3c&H533D32&}No, I'll go first..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:25.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,(Announcer) So, today's guest from\NToshiminami Psychiatric University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,was Dr. Hino Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:29.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was well said, Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:32.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This will also,\Nraise our popularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the number of examinees and the income\Nwill have a sudden increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's wicked, Hasumi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I just think that it can contribute\Nto the psychiatric development
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that's why I recommended him to the TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa-kun, don't you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:48.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Something as Hino-kun's bestseller\Nto take out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:51.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, no,\NI ..something like this..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:58.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:01.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,, Oh ~again ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:17.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.61,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Would you stay close, from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:25.87,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:28.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where did you go this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:31.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For a walk.\N{\3c&H533D32&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The weather is good.\NDid you feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow is the performance\Nof "Higashi Odori", you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's do it stylish.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Refreshing and stylish!\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NWe will ask for your appearance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then with your permission.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:48.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good work.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.85,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino!\NDr. Hino, please your autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:53.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor\Nhas plans after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.82,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, give him some space.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. Kawakami-kun,\Nmy bag, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And also I have this.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These are fan letters.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's gone.\NBut.. he's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:25.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:27.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, listen..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:33.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That psychiatrist that is your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you know what he told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:39.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That it was better for me not to be here..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.35,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's the same as telling me to die, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He wants to apart us, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:46.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:49.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mom can't live without\Nseeing you..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,how about the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\3c&H533D32&}The 10 million I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:04.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't get them soon,\NI may be killed for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It means that mom is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,we don't have any relation with the doctor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand that..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm back, we've returned.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., you forgot your cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, it was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Akira.\NI went for a walk early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your message.\NYou can send another again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:16.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please contact at any time you need.\NWe'll have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. that..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your phone was ringing non-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be..a stalker?\N{\3c&H533D32&}No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You know, this is..\N{\3c&H533D32&}Kaoru-san..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is for your son. \N{\3c&H533D32&}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Look, the drawing that you showed me,\Nhe is really skillful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.\NIt's so luxurious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shinya will be very happy. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?\N{\3c&H533D32&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:52.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:56.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?\NStop meddling with Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:00.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't keep your promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll make Hino-rin's life a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, just fine. I'm really hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for choosing us! Here's Makoto sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here are the first class 30 servings.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Dr. Hino,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you ask it? Sushi.\N{\3c&H533D32&}No, I didn't ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What? We received an order from Kawakami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I did not make such a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're beaten, a prank call?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well..since you took the trouble, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh.. Thank you very much!\N{\3c&H533D32&}How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is ¥ 97,200. (~802.70 USD)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,¥ 97,200!??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:42.60,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.11,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:50.56,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.08,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:06:02.11,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:06.61,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:17.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, they don't know who ask for the sushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who would eat such thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. please, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.!\N{\3c&H533D32&}What! You should knock when entering a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I did..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh this is Dr. Hino's book.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Well it ....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think this book is funny\N{\3c&H533D32&}I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Know your enemy, know thyself,\Nand you shall not fear a hundred battles"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:19.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't really get that,\Nbut if you like sushi, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It seems it was ordered excessively,\Nso, we're sharing portions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. from whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's from Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I wonder why\Ndid they use Kawakami-san's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-san, do you have any idea?\N..you're not listening..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:40.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah! Could it be that geisha\Nnamed Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It may be!\NSince she borrowed Dr. Hino's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If there is some kind of trouble ....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:47.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is no evidence of that!\N{\3c&H533D32&}So you were listening..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor told you clearly, right?\Nthat is bad to judge something by guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that means that Kawakami-san, you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,also suspects from Yumeno-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right now, you definitely were listening..\NHang in there, Daisaku
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:05.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A lecture of Dr. Hino,\Nwhen I hear the doctor's voice, feels like healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.44,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Your mother was a woman like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.44,Remembering,,0,0,0,,sluttish with men
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:28.08,Remembering,,0,0,0,,This mom with such an elegant face
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.80,Remembering,,0,0,0,,had an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:50.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..Hello, Araki senpai,\NIs it okay if I stop by today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah..It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And I have a sort of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you buy me the usual\Nin a hurry and bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:06.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What our Yumeno did was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:18.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has Yumeno come back?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:26.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, suddenly her condition became worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:31.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even so, isn't the recent Yumeno a little strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:36.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be because our Hino-kun, I wonder..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Never such a thing ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:46.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is also Minister Ike's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If Yumeno acts weird it will be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't put me to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:08.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, right, the tickets left for "Azuma Odori"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll buy them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here's Hoshino Yoshimi-san, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Hoshino Yoshimi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, my name is Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:33.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what seems to be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:49.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All the time, someone is following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Someone..follows you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's an unknown man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely sure he followed me today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm scare, can't bear this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is scary, I'm sure.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Every day I'm worried about\Nbeing killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm also scared of crowds,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't go outside at night either,\NI'm scared of watched behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:18.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see, have you discussed this with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:22.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My parents don't believe my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is no one who can defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:31.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san, why don't you take this\Nto the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want to. I don't rely on something as the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:41.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, in the future, if you feel like\Nsomeone is following you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,while talking loudly on your phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please move to the place where\Nthere are people who you can ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At any rate,\Njust be resolved to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:52.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Go out with your family and people you can trust on..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:59.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is no such person! That's why\NI came to see Dr. Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If something happens, please help me.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:12.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.\Nyou will not forsake me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:19.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you feel some anxiety.\NPlease contact me at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:22.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:27.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see, as expected you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,when she talked about your mother,\Nyou lose your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:30.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:34.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh.. thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:37.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Seeing you with an usual average heart\Nit's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That shows how serious you are about this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can tell because of that..right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those last words you retorted to her..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.60,Remembering,,0,0,0,,A mother like you,\Nshould better disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:02.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, you are that serious\Nabout saving that geisha's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:13.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,then, just don't care about\Nhow Ennoji thinks anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Only about what you have to do!\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Senpai.\N{\3c&H533D32&}what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can I have something salty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You, don't go and open anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That, don't open that, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, you're able to come, Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just that..all the Dr.'s contact data is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come inside\Nand talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke, I'm back~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for disturbing.\N{\3c&H533D32&}I'm back..~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, there's something I want\Nto ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to answer, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:57.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Similarly as today, that all your cellphone contact data\Nis gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Has this ever happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..not just the contact data..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:09.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,things like personal belongings\Nhave increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How long has this been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For about 8 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,8 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:27.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At that time, did something important happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to answer..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:36.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A little before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my mother appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She wanted me to help her,\Nsince she was having financial problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She told me to become a geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:52.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, you quit your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:57.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At that time, mom\Ntold me for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that once I've made a lot of money,\Nwe'll live together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:08.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She said, "This time, Akira-chan\Nwill surely be happy"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yet, I couldn't earn much money at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:20.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And mom's debts have\Nrapidly increased,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,even though mom was trying her best,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:28.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've been nothing but just a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:33.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san,\Nyou're not at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Around the time\Nyour mobile data disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,anything strange happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Somehow I came to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:04.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that Yumeno, who occasionally speaks\Nfrom the back of my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,was the one doing all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:12.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She has been earning the money\Nin order to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:19.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,During her time, my time disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'm going to disappear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,On your birthday, we even went to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Anything you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:08.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your daily events,\Nthe things you feel or think,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,little by little, in this notebook,\Nwhy don't you write them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, I will serve you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:21.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,as to connect the time\Nbetween you and Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to connect both of our times?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:50.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a dangerous thing to lose the reasoning power\Nto a thing called love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though during the course of the treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:56.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,feelings similar to those of love arise,\Neventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:02.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the patient is treated to the point when\N they love someone else than the therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:07.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's the psychiatrist's job\Nto lead them to a happier life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:46.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:49.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Inhale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:54.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,While picturing it.\NBreath slowly..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:20:01.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Continue with a long exhalation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It has become a lot easier.\N{\3c&H533D32&}It has. I am happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:18.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:22.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The patient Hoshino Yoshimi-sama\Nwants to talk with Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, but\Nthe doctor now it's in the middle of a consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you can talk to me instead,\NI'm Dr. Kawakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san, what is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Put Dr. Hino on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:49.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm being targeted by a stalker\NPlease quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please calm down.\NIs the stalker nearby you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm calling you because he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone near\Nyou can ask for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:21:00.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's none,  because there's no one\NI'm calling Dr. Hino
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:04.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor is really busy now,\Nfirst, let's call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't bear your talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:10.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:24.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you become anxious...remember\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino! Just now, Hoshino-san called you.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because she said she was being chased by a stalker\NI told her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to contact the police,\Nbut she hung up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-san\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:44.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please leave your\Nmessage after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:51.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san, it's Hino from\Nthe Toshiminami University Hospital, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:54.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If something happens, please contact me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:21:59.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the future, when a patient issues an SOS\Ncall
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please don't absolutely, \Nserve such answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:07.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:10.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Whenever there is a call from Hoshino-san,\Npass it on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:13.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please communicated this to the doctor of the night shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:19.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh ... I am still not there yet..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:27.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, it's great, isn't it?\NThis thesis, finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:29.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's right.\N{\3c&H533D32&}I regularly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:32.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,listen to Dr. Hino's recordings,\Nin order not to miss one word.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've also read his book\Nand memorize it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it took me one year to complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:41.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like you are in love with Dr. Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:43.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, I really like him.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The one called Yumeno,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:49.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mainly the face of the geisha,\Nowns the main personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:51.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The one called Akira,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:55.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the one who is in the process of opening her heart,\Nthe original personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:58.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in other words, that means she is the one born into the body.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:01.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, how do you intend to treat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:07.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In her case, to make the two personalities,\Nrecognize and align mutually
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's a good way to achieve\Nthe integration process.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,While respecting both personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:15.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the treatment must advance\Nwith a consistent attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:17.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, to achieve this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:20.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The presence of the mother is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:23.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A gambling-dependent mother, right?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:27.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the relationship of codependency formed with the daughter,\Nthat's a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:31.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:35.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,sorry to bother you so late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:37.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:44.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:50.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:58.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Ikumi-sa ~n.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What do you want at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for disturbing.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:03.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:10.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.08,0:24:12.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Call them if you want..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:16.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san!\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:18.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:25.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're treating me like a stalker,\NI'm her mother, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:27.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You often say so, but..\N{\3c&H533D32&}Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:30.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is your biggest earner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:32.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what a good money-spinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:33.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:36.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've always tormented that child!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:38.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That child has become like this because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.90,0:24:44.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't give that scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.89,0:24:49.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was bad ....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.41,0:24:51.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.89,0:24:54.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you know, I ..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.89,0:24:58.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to start again for real..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.98,0:25:01.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,this time….
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:04.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,from the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.40,0:25:07.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,changing from the heart..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.89,0:25:11.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to start over with her, as a parent and child..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.38,0:25:21.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These are Akira-san's favorite candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.39,0:25:23.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,could you..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.39,0:25:27.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,could you do me the favor\Nof giving this to her..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:30.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You do not change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.40,0:25:33.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When the circumstances get bad
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.72,0:25:36.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you suddenly shed meek tears,\Nas looking sad..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.76,0:25:39.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You won't fool me anymore!\N{\3c&H533D32&}What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:41.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.39,0:25:44.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not show your face again!\N{\3c&H533D32&}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.92,0:25:49.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,do you... you\Ndo you think you're protecting that child?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.92,0:25:52.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san..\Nyou're here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:55.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're listening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.08,0:25:58.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,next time, both of us,\Nwe are going to start over~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.48,0:26:00.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Leave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.44,0:26:02.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, I'll come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.76,0:26:05.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother...\N{\3c&H533D32&}LEAVE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.60,0:26:07.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.84,0:26:14.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.56,0:26:17.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:38.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've told you, the same as always, I'll gain the money\Nto help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.88,0:26:44.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just forget already about that psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.40,0:27:20.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.41,0:27:21.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.89,0:27:25.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.36,0:27:54.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving to the conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.39,0:27:56.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.38,0:28:03.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.60,0:28:06.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is Dr. Hino in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.72,0:28:10.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you knock before coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:14.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, when\Nwill he be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.96,0:28:16.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where should I wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:19.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but the doctor\Nis in his day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.92,0:28:25.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is a difficult case,\Nhowever, for Dr. Hasumi..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:29.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Tonight, the director has invited me, for The Azuma Odori\Nat Shinbashi, if you want to come..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.41,0:28:31.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:35.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.39,0:28:44.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. Rintaro.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.41,0:28:46.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Look..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.56,0:28:50.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. right, I heard that last night you all went to drink, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:53.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Was there something unusual about Kawakami-kun?\N{\3c&H533D32&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.84,0:28:56.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that a while ago,\Nshe was acting strange
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.48,0:28:59.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mm..maybe something is bothering her..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.64,0:29:01.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,having received a warning from her beloved Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.89,0:29:03.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.39,0:29:05.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:10.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Brother?\NThis is bad, Yasuke has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.04,0:29:12.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke is not there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.16,0:29:15.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's more, the house is a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.88,0:29:19.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All right...well..\NI'll return immediately after I've finished
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.40,0:29:22.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,afternoon examination.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What happened to Yasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.40,0:29:24.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke\Nseems to have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.32,0:29:25.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.38,0:29:27.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be?\Nthe same person that order the sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.90,0:29:30.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll go look for Yasuke.\N{\3c&H533D32&}No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:32.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since, I'm done here for today, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.41,0:29:38.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka-chan. \N{\3c&H533D32&}Yuriko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.38,0:29:42.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Whoa..it's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.40,0:29:45.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that geisha did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.39,0:29:51.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.91,0:29:54.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, we should start preparing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.91,0:29:58.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where could Yumeno go?\NIn such an important day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.48,0:30:10.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.28,0:30:20.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not around here.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.89,0:30:22.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,good grief.. 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.88,0:30:26.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try asking that person there.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.38,0:30:29.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me but, have you seen around here..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:31.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a white and of this size..{\u1}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.94,0:30:36.94,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, to make you come.\N{\3c&H533D32&}No
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.37,0:30:40.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go look on that way.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Okay, I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.04,0:30:48.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-san! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.84,0:30:51.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize to Dr. Hino.\N{\3c&H533D32&}Now it's a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.52,0:30:53.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait.. Fukuhara-san
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.96,0:30:59.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:02.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. sorry Mizushima. How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.00,0:31:04.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Bad, he's nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.88,0:31:12.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.91,0:31:14.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.38,0:31:19.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.38,0:31:21.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.37,0:31:22.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.87,0:31:29.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.88,0:31:39.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to gain,\Nby doing such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.87,0:31:41.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is your grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.89,0:31:44.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The rubbish scattered at home, that\Nwas also you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.37,0:31:46.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka, calm down.\N{\3c&H533D32&}What are you trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.39,0:31:48.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka.\N{\3c&H533D32&}But!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.36,0:31:50.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you take care of Yasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.37,0:31:59.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.37,0:32:00.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.39,0:32:06.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.88,0:32:09.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.36,0:32:14.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Was it Yumeno, right? Yumeno was angry,\Nand did that to Yasuke..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:18.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.86,0:32:29.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san is not the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.36,0:32:31.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today she came to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.52,0:32:36.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She wanted to see the doctor,\Nbut the fact is that I sent her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.76,0:32:37.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.95,0:32:41.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, that was what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:48.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, why did you go to the examining room?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.37,0:32:52.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.39,0:32:54.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your hand..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.88,0:33:01.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If the perpetrator\Nisn't Yumeno-san, then..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.87,0:33:08.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kawakami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.38,0:33:13.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.39,0:33:31.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The doctor\Nborrowed this diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.37,0:33:40.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor's laughing face.. is difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.48,0:33:48.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sky is blue and the leaves are green..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.00,0:33:51.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}now is the season I like the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.37,0:34:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(433.6,31.6)}[T/N]: she has the word "TRAITOR" written all over her body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:14.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard the sound of the sea with the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:17.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it still remains in my ears even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.38,0:34:30.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.16,0:34:33.46,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found a four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.88,0:34:39.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to make him laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.88,0:34:42.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want the doctor to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.37,0:34:47.86,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that Dr. Rintaro's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.86,0:34:49.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.32,0:34:54.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\3c&H533D32&}She seems nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.16,0:34:57.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.16,0:35:04.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Rintaro, even now, is trying to cure..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.88,0:35:08.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,his mother's mind disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.16,0:35:17.38,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Dr. Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.44,0:35:21.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, don't worry,\NYumechiyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.24,0:35:25.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes. She's fine.\NOkay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.16,0:35:28.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, since I've finished, I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.12,0:35:29.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really?\NNow, I'm doing some tea..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.04,0:35:36.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was necessary for you, to tell her\Neven about your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.76,0:35:42.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's also treatment, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:49.37,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, l'll let you talk\Ncarefully with Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.24,0:35:50.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.76,0:35:56.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.40,0:35:58.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.87,0:36:17.87,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.32,0:36:37.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I must apologize to Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.00,0:36:43.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a result, Yumeno-san got angry
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.01,0:36:45.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and you were the one that got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.49,0:36:48.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.48,0:37:00.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, said she wanted to see\Nme, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.24,0:37:10.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, from next week on,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.55,0:37:14.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why don't you come with Yumechiyo-san\Nto the examining room?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.99,0:37:21.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Am I that much bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.51,0:37:24.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is something that I'm still not able to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.50,0:37:27.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All I can say now, is that inside of you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.28,0:37:31.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,there are two different persons, Akira-san and Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.49,0:37:35.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then through medical examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.07,0:37:38.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,talking not just with you,\Nbut also with Yumeno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.01,0:37:41.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,inquiring more and more\Nabout you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.16,0:37:45.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, that means
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.16,0:37:48.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that we can't meet again like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.56,0:38:00.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We can still have a good talk at the examining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.02,0:38:10.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the Okiya today.\N{\3c&H533D32&}It's okay, I'll return alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.49,0:38:11.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.51,0:38:16.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because who I am now..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.92,0:38:22.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to say goodbye to the doctor as Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.52,0:38:33.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.02,0:38:43.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you hold me tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:59.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, please remember one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.53,0:39:02.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.51,0:39:08.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A~lways\NI'll be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.01,0:39:23.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, I have something to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.40,0:39:26.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:27.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.00,0:39:33.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., it's about Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.01,0:39:35.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that medical treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.06,0:39:40.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or is it... love?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:41.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.00,0:39:47.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., aren't you in love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.92,0:39:55.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.60,0:40:00.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.51,0:40:16.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kawakami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:19.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, now it's not possible
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.51,0:40:23.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for me to accept your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.01,0:40:40.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.51,0:40:43.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.50,0:40:48.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,With this refreshing feeling\NI'll be able to do the examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.07,0:40:50.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.01,0:40:55.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.51,0:40:59.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., here is Hoshino Yoshimi-san.\NCome in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.55,0:41:08.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.51,0:41:16.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.50,0:41:22.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be in charge,\Nmy name is Kawakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.50,0:41:26.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?\NDr. Hino is the one on charge, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.02,0:41:27.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why are you in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.24,0:41:29.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and call the Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.72,0:41:33.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go home if you don't call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.56,0:41:37.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's you who vandalized Dr. Hino's house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.50,0:41:43.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.04,0:41:50.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These, I've read these.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.16,0:41:53.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you have them?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.16,0:41:55.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san,\Nplease listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.40,0:42:00.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I also,\Nhave fallen in love with people I admire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.99,0:42:03.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't make us even!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.51,0:42:07.03,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I also fell deeply in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.03,0:42:10.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I listened to his voice hundreds of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.40,0:42:12.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And even though I knew I shouldn't do it..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.50,0:42:16.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I also stood in front of his house many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.03,0:42:25.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I was a child, I was really selfish,\Ndidn't have friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.51,0:42:28.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I really hated myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.55,0:42:34.05,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"I want to be different", that was always in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.01,0:42:38.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm the same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.50,0:42:46.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I also, after meeting Dr. Hino,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.00,0:42:49.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,felt as if I was reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.00,0:43:05.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"January 14 \NI read Dr. Hino's book,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.50,0:43:09.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and now, I also want to change."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:12.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I was little,\NI was clueless and bad at reading situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.53,0:43:15.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and became hated by everyone."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:31.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"February 3\NToday I saw Dr. Hino on TV."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.00,0:43:34.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&H533D32&}"There is not such thing as perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.00,0:43:37.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&H533D32&}a passing mark without a perfect score is fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.52,0:43:40.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&H533D32&}To think like this is fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.57,0:43:43.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I was worried about a thing at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.51,0:43:46.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was really saved by the doctor's words. "
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.01,0:44:03.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"March 6. Today too,\NI watched Dr. Hino on TV"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.01,0:44:06.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&H533D32&}"When you lose your confidence ... "
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.01,0:44:08.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&H533D32&}each day,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:13.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&H533D32&}"please, try to find one positive thing about yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.51,0:44:20.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"By doing so after a month, you will become self-confident."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.68,0:44:28.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san, you in this way, always
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.56,0:44:30.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,have been receiving important things from the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.84,0:44:33.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because you want to\Nproperly start over that you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.99,0:44:37.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, if you continue this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.16,0:44:42.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the important words taught by the Dr.,\Nand lots of warm words,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.84,0:44:45.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,don't you feel like you'll lose all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.51,0:44:52.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Falling in love with someone\Nwho doesn't return your feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.01,0:44:54.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.01,0:44:58.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But losing the important things you received from\Nthe person you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.52,0:45:00.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think it's even more painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:07.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san,\Nthe feelings when falling in love with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.99,0:45:10.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,are in no way something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.00,0:45:20.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Won't you make a fresh start in life,\Nagain, together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.03,0:45:28.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If so then,\Nplease call Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.64,0:45:33.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please, let me hear his voice just once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.50,0:45:42.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.53,0:45:44.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.56,0:45:49.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.00,0:45:50.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.76,0:46:03.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.16,0:46:09.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I talk first?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.51,0:46:17.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was looking for my dog desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:21.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For you it might be only another person's pet, but
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.02,0:46:27.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,but for me, he is an irreplaceable\Nimportant family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.44,0:46:31.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the same way as that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.01,0:46:34.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I inherited that house from my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.51,0:46:36.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I treasure being able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.00,0:46:43.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It may be old, but it's full of family memories\Nfrom my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.52,0:46:47.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's a precious house for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.06,0:46:52.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Such house,\Nyou have dishonored.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.52,0:46:58.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm very hurt by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.01,0:47:05.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hoshino-san, do you have something to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.08,0:47:13.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.52,0:47:17.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.09,0:47:41.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.00,0:47:43.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.96,0:47:57.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I suspect that Hoshino-san has a mild form of\Nborderline personality disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.72,0:48:00.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and factitious disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.50,0:48:05.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If the healer wants to reach the patient\Nwith his words, in this case
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.00,0:48:08.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's important to convey that by stalking the other party,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.16,0:48:10.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she has personally hurt the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.53,0:48:14.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and to communicate this very clearly\Nbut in a polite way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.72,0:48:17.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If she is allowed to calmly understand the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.24,0:48:20.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the patient can be discouraged from continuing such behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.52,0:48:22.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, surely, Hoshino-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.52,0:48:25.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,will be able to make a new step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.51,0:48:34.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for doing something\Narbitrary today.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.07,0:48:36.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.50,0:48:40.49,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, to reach the patient with the attitude\Ninstead of making them
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.49,0:48:43.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,remained cornered,\NI think it was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.01,0:48:48.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think that approach shook\N Hoshino-san's feelings, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.68,0:48:52.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a party of the stalking incident, I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.55,0:48:55.55,Default 1,,0,0,0,,can't carry out Hoshino-san's treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.99,0:48:59.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kawakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.51,0:49:03.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving Hoshino-san under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.51,0:49:08.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, continue to get closer\Nto her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.50,0:49:11.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.52,0:49:14.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are no final answers in medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.09,0:49:17.99,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When doubting or when troubled,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.99,0:49:22.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,continue to listen to the voice of the patient's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.01,0:49:26.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think that's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.00,0:49:29.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From now on, I have my hopes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.01,0:49:34.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.01,0:49:40.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.52,0:49:48.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you have a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.99,0:49:52.53,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.53,0:49:54.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.56,0:50:11.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.01,0:50:13.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.02,0:50:18.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, I'll leave her under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.04,0:50:21.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumechiyo-san,\Nplease wait at the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.59,0:50:23.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.50,0:50:33.50,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hi, Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.50,0:50:36.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.00,0:50:38.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.52,0:50:41.02,Default 1,,0,0,0,,could you hold me tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.51,0:50:44.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
